translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「パランナイツはヘルマンやリーザスにも負けない、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "The Palannights have skill and training that rival even Helman and Leesas,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 素晴らしい練度と聞きました。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I have heard their proficiency is outstanding.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: きちんと確認させて頂きます」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I would like to properly confirm that."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「どうぞ、存分に」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Go ahead, as much as you wish."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「あのう……すみません。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Um… excuse me.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: パランチョ王国って、どんな国なんですか？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: What kind of country is the Kingdom of Paranco?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 私、聞いたことなくて……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I've never heard of it before..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「なんだ、知らんのかお前。不勉強だな」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "What, you don't know? That's unstudious of you."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「うっ……ランス様はご存じなんですか？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Ugh... Lord Rance, do you know about it?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「俺が知るわけ無いだろう。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "There's no way I would know.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: どうせ豆粒みたいな国だ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It's probably just a tiny, insignificant country anyway."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ら、ランス様っ……！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "L-Lord Rance...!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ピッテンさんがいるのに……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Even though Pitten-san is here..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「豆粒か。言い得て妙かもしれんな」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "A tiny speck, huh? That might be an apt description."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「あの、すみません……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Um, excuse me..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「パランチョは……そうだな。こんな国だ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Paranco is... well, it's a country like this."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ピッテンが手を拍つと、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: When Pitten clapped his hands,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 従者がひとつのザルを持ってきた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: A servant brought over a basket.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「……なんだこりゃ？　豆か？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "...What is this? Beans?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「少し囓ってみろ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Try nibbling on one."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ただの石とかだったら頭カチ割るからな……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "If it's just a stone or something, I'll crack your head open...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ん、んん……っ、げほっ、辛っ！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Mmm, mmm... *cough* Spicy!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「あ、これ……香辛料のピリン豆、ですか？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Ah, this... is this 'Pirin Beans,' the spice?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: たまに、お店ですごい値段で売ってますけど……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Sometimes it's sold at shops for an incredible price..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「うちの国の名産でな。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "It's a specialty product of our country.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 価値はあるが採れるのは少量だ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It has value, but only a small amount can be harvested."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「……なるほど。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "...I see.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 確かに、パランチョはそんな国ですね」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Indeed, Paranco is that kind of country."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「まぁ、そんなところだ。ではな」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Well, that's about it. Farewell."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 口元に笑みを少しだけ浮かべると、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: With a slight smile at the corner of his mouth,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ピッテンはマントを翻して退出した。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Pitten flipped his cloak and exited.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ちっ。雑魚なのを誤魔化す為に、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Tch. Saying nonsense just to cover up how weak they are...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 訳の分からん事言いやがって……ぺぺっ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: What a bunch of nonsense... pfft."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「そ、そうではないと思いますけど……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "I-I don't think that's the case though..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「しかし、ここはいつも賑やかだな……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Still, it's always lively here...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 城主のせいか」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Maybe because of the lord of the castle."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ピッテンは、所用でランス城にやって来ていた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Pitten had come to Rance Castle on some business.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「そ、そんな！　ひどいです、ランス兄様！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "N-No way! That's terrible, Brother Rance!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「食後に甘い物があると良いって言ってたから、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "You said it would be nice to have something sweet after the meal,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 作ったのにー！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: so I made some!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ぐっ……だがその……団子じゃないか！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Ugh... but, that's... dango, isn't it!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 今日は一段と、色艶が……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Today it looks even more colorful and glossy..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「い、いつものがダメだって言うから、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Y-You said the usual one was no good,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 少し変えてみたんです！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: so I tried changing it a bit!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「死ぬ……これは死ぬぞ！　人類が滅ぶ！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "I'm going to die... This will kill me! Humanity will perish!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「わーん！　そ、そこまで言わなくても……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Waaah! Y-You don't have to say it that way..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「意外だな。ランスが少女の願いを無碍にする類の
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Surprising. I didn't think Rance was the type to harshly reject a girl's wish.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 人間とは思わなかったが」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: But I guess I was wrong."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ああん！？　金ぴか野郎か！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Huh!? You shiny-golden guy!"
